    "causal_summary": "Phase parent for a new benchmark hosted in the deep-alignment mode that measures the OpenCode command surface on two non-averaged axes: a deterministic full-corpus peer adapter (sk-doc-command) auditing structural command integrity across all 37 commands, and a sampled behavioral DAB suite (DAB-012–027 on the shared behavior-benchmark framework v2) that actually invokes commands and scores adherence. A bounded model matrix (Claude baseline + gpt-5.6-sol + gpt-5.6-luna-fast) measures executor variance only, not the benchmark itself.",
